A Sombrero trace recorder is a way to record traces for later use. A recorder
most provide the following interfaces.

Recording interface:

	Recorder.makeLiteral(val)
	Recorder.makeFunction(name, argnames)
	Recorder.makeComputation(func, args)
	Recorder.enterComputation(obj)
	Recorder.finishComputation(obj, result)

Reading interface:

	A Program object, with all that entails.
